%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22France's%20army%20chief%20says%20small%20drones%20will%20lose%20their%20battlefield%20advantage.%20But%20Ukraine%20won't%20be%20changing%20tack%20anytime%20soon.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20%26quot%3BGhost%26quot%3B%20air%20reconnaissance%20unit%20of%20Ukraine's%20Main%20Directorate%20of%20Intelligence%20(HUR)%20keeps%20defense%20on%20the%20Vovchansk%20area%20on%20May%2019%2C%202024%2C%20in%20Kharkiv%20Oblast%2C%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667e9b3bd1c84a0eaca8994c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20reconnaissance%20unit%20in%20Kharkiv%20Oblast.%3Cp%3EGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESmall%20drones%20dominate%20Ukraine's%20battlefield%2C%20but%20their%20advantage%20won't%20last%2C%20France's%20army%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESmall%2C%20relatively%20cheap%20drones%20have%20been%20hugely%20successful%20weapons%20in%20the%20war%20so%20far.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20advancing%20countermeasures%20would%20limit%20small%20drones'%20capabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20aerial%20drones%20have%20dominated%20the%20battlefield%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20according%20to%20French%20Army%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Gen.%20Pierre%20Schill%2C%20they%20could%20soon%20lose%20their%20combat%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Eurosatory%20defense%20show%20in%20Paris%20on%20June%2019%2C%20Schill%20said%20that%20their%20advantage%20represented%20merely%20%26quot%3Ba%20moment%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fglobal%2Feurope%2F2024%2F06%2F19%2Fsmall-drones-will-soon-lose-combat-advantage-french-army-chief-says%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefense%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20life%20of%20impunity%20of%20small%2C%20very%20simple%20drones%20over%20the%20battlefield%20is%20a%20snapshot%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Schill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%20it's%20being%20exploited%2C%20that's%20clear%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20protect%20ourselves.%20Today%2C%20the%20sword%2C%20in%20the%20sense%20of%20the%20aerial%20drone%2C%20is%20powerful%2C%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20shield.%20The%20shield%20is%20going%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225580%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20head%20of%20the%20French%20Army%2C%20General%20d'armee%20Pierre%20Schill%20inspects%20the%20officer%20cadets%20during%20Commissioning%20Course%20No.%20232%20Sovereign's%20Parade%2C%20at%20the%20Royal%20Military%20Academy%20Sandhurst%2C%20southwest%20of%20London%20on%20April%2012%2C%202024%2C%20to%20mark%20the%20120th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Entente%20Cordiale.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667ec4d3d1c84a0eaca8a6da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20head%20of%20the%20French%20army%2C%20Pierre%20Schill.%3Cp%3EADRIAN%20DENNIS%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292c5bc36-569f-417c-b133-1b2046994f21%5C%22%3EThe%20use%20of%20drones%20will%20likely%20fluctuate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20British%20Army%20officer%20Christopher%20Lincoln-Jones%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20use%20of%20small%20drones%20in%20warfare%20would%20likely%20%26quot%3Bebb%20and%20flow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20happen%20is%20that%2C%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%20becomes%20better%20and%20better%20and%20the%20senses%20become%20better%2C%20medium-sized%20drones%20will%20dominate%20rather%20than%20the%20small%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMini%20drones%20are%20limited%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20battery%20technology%20is%20not%20good%20enough%20for%20them%20yet.%20And%20although%20they%20can%20carry%20a%20small%20charge%20or%20weapon%2C%20they're%20not%20really%20good%20against%20military%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20Lincoln-Jones%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Bagwell%2C%20the%20UK%20Royal%20Air%20Force's%20former%20Deputy%20Commander%2C%20told%20BI%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20some%20truth%26quot%3B%20to%20Schill's%20comments%20about%20the%20future%20of%20small%20drones%20in%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20to%20say%20it's%20nearly%20had%20its%20day%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20over%20is%20probably%20a%20slight%20exaggeration.%20But%20I%20think%20it%20will%20get%20harder%20for%20them%20to%20operate%20as%20people%20now%20get%20wise%20to%20this%20threat.%20We'll%20start%20to%20see%20the%20counters%20maybe%20begin%20to%20take%20a%20higher%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a11ea6ca-f69a-4247-8160-212e162d2917%5C%22%3ESmall%20drones%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20drones%2C%20particularly%20first-person%20view%20drones%20(FPVs)%2C%20have%20been%20a%20trademark%20of%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20weaponizing%20them%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFPV%20drones%20have%20had%20huge%20success%20on%20the%20battlefield%20so%20far%2C%20proving%20to%20be%20cheaper%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fgraphics%2FUKRAINE-CRISIS%2FDRONES%2Fdwpkeyjwkpm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20accurate%20than%20most%20artillery%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20can%20be%20guided%20directly%20to%20their%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2024%2F04%2F09%2Fdrones-russia-tanks-ukraine-war-fpv-artillery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENATO%20official%20told%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20that%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20Russian%20tanks%20that%20had%20been%20destroyed%20by%20Ukraine%20in%20recent%20months%20had%20been%20targeted%20with%20FPVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-drone-liutyi-behind-majority-ukraine-attacks-russia-oil-facilities-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epounded%20Russian%20oil%20refineries%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-mass-attack-russian-airbase-70-drones-budanov-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairbases%20with%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20a%20widespread%20campaign%20to%20disrupt%20Russian%20military%20supplies%20and%20hamper%20the%20Russian%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227279dc38-4a79-447d-9442-f4b246c9aaa8%5C%22%3EDrone%20countermeasures%20are%20advancing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Lincoln-Jones%20and%20Bagwell%20both%20echoed%20Gen.%20Schill's%20warnings%20that%20drone%20countermeasures%20are%20advancing%20and%20would%20increasingly%20render%20small%20drones%20less%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20all%20sorts%20of%20techniques%20being%20used%20to%20jam%20the%20signals%2C%20the%20video%2C%20or%20the%20GPS%20signal%2C%26quot%3B%20Bagwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchill%20said%20that%20electronic%20warfare%20%E2%80%94%20which%20uses%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%2C%20including%20signals%20like%20radio%2C%20infrared%2C%20or%20radar%2C%20to%20disrupt%20an%20enemy's%20ability%20to%20use%20those%20signals%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20was%20already%20neutralizing%2075%25%20of%20drones%20deployed%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20you%20can%20encrypt%20and%20use%20direct%20line%20of%20sight%20to%20control%20your%20drone%2C%20you're%20very%20vulnerable%20to%20nearly%20every%20electronic%20warfare%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Lincoln-Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20just%20need%20to%20know%20what%20frequency%20the%20drone%20is%20operating%20on%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20its%20commands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20current%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%20being%20used%20to%20defend%20against%20drone%20attacks%20have%20their%20limits.%20The%20use%20of%20such%20systems%20risks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-using-electronic-warfare-ukraine-against-drones-means-killing-internet-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterfering%20with%20other%20technology%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlanticcouncil.org%2Fblogs%2Fnew-atlanticist%2Fthe-drones-are-small-the-arms-race-may-not-be-heres-how-the-us-can-win%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eradios%20and%20cellphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20in%20the%20drone's%20vicinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrone%20production%20also%20continues%20to%20surge%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20spite%20of%20increasing%20defense%20systems%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pravda.com.ua%2Feng%2Fnews%2F2024%2F02%2F1%2F7439866%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20200%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20producing%20aerial%20drones%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20are%20now%20also%20pumping%20money%20into%20developing%20AI-powered%20drones%20that%20can%20bypass%20electronic%20warfare%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20seems%20that%20small%20drone%20warfare%20won't%20be%20going%20away%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen.%20Schill%20declined%20an%20interview%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-drones-fpv-ukraine-russia-warfare-military-future-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719661751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667e9b8140cf2af6e4f687ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-drones-fpv-ukraine-russia-warfare-military-future-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%