-general-doctor-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraw%20(unpasteurized)%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20on%20the%20surfaces%20of%20materials%20used%20in%20equipment%20for%20milking%20dairy%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20clue%20in%20the%20mystery%20of%20how%20the%20virus%20has%20spread%20so%20rapidly%20between%20US%20dairy%20cattle%2C%20infecting%20over%20130%20herds%20in%20Idaho%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Colorado%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cattle%20outbreak%20has%20scientists%20increasingly%20worried%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh5n1-bird-flu-virus-experts-concerned-human-outbreak-spread-possible-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH5N1%20virus%20could%20mutate%3C%2Fa%3E%20enough%20to%20cause%20an%20outbreak%20in%20humans.%20The%20more%20the%20virus%20spreads%20through%20cattle%2C%20the%20more%20opportunity%20it%20has%20to%20mutate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22h5n1%20virus%20microscope%20image%20shows%20black%20and%20white%20long%20straight%20worm-shaped%20organism%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669b8e2e079049018182611%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20avian%20influenza%20A%20H5N1%20virion%2C%20viewed%20through%20an%20electron%20microscope.%3Cp%3ECynthia%20Goldsmith%2C%20Jackie%20Katz%2FCDC%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20April%2C%20three%20farmworkers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-virus-h5n1-new-human-case-michigan-respiratory-symptoms-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etested%20positive%20for%20the%20virus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20experts%20have%20found%20no%20evidence%20of%20human-to-human%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20how%20the%20virus%20spreads%20between%20cattle%20is%20key%20to%20reigning%20in%20the%20outbreak%20and%20preventing%20further%20human%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20know%20which%20dairy%20herds%20are%20infected%2C%20with%20what%20strains%20of%20virus%2C%20how%20infection%20is%20spread%20between%20farms%2C%20and%20how%20frequently%20dairy%20farm%20workers%20and%20other%20people%20are%20exposed%2C%26quot%3B%20Christopher%20Dye%2C%20an%20infectious%20disease%20expert%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Falerts-advisories-safety-information%2Fupdates-highly-pathogenic-avian-influenza-hpai%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520our%2520May%252010%2520update%2Con%2520our%2520retail%2520sample%2520survey.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pasteurized%20milk%20purchased%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%20remains%20safe%20to%20drink.%20However%2C%20raw%20milk%20could%20be%20an%20agent%20of%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22717db34b-2baa-40b1-9ee3-63df82ce7055%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20to%20help%20stop%20the%20spread%20of%20H5N1%20bird%20flu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222062%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22racecar%20driver%20wearing%20red%20firestone%20cap%20with%20wreath%20of%20flowers%20over%20shoulders%20chugs%20milk%20from%20a%20glass%20bottle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662acb4610dfcda409639e0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDriver%20Tony%20Kanaan%20of%20Brazil%20takes%20the%20traditional%20drink%20of%20milk%20after%20winning%20the%2097th%20running%20of%20the%20Indianapolis%20500%20at%20the%20Indianapolis%20Motor%20Speedway.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Haynes%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20already%20knew%20that%20H5N1%20was%20jumping%20farm-to-farm%20through%20the%20movement%20of%20cows%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20people%20and%20that%20the%20virus%20concentrates%20in%20sick%20cows'%20udders%20and%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20means%20even%20just%20a%20small%20splash%20of%20milk%20can%20spread%20the%20disease%2C%26quot%3B%20Secretary%20of%20Agriculture%20Tom%20Vilsack%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.agri-pulse.com%2Farticles%2F21271-opinion-good-biosecurity-is-the-key-to-mitigating-the-spread-of-h5n1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eop-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20new%20study%20found%20that%20H5N1%20virus%20remained%20infectious%20in%20raw%20milk%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20on%20stainless%20steel%20and%20rubber%20inflation%20lining%20%E2%80%94%20material%20used%20in%20milking%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwwwnc.cdc.gov%2Feid%2Farticle%2F30%2F8%2F24-0775_article%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20journal%20Emerging%20Infectious%20Diseases%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilk%20may%20not%20be%20the%20only%20transmission%20route.%20It's%20possible%20that%20cows%20infect%20each%20other%20by%20licking%20each%20other%20or%20shoving%20their%20heads%20into%20feed%20together%2C%20for%20example%2C%20according%20to%20Meghan%20Davis%2C%20an%20epidemiologist%20at%20the%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Bloomberg%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20and%20former%20dairy%20veterinarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20study%20suggests%20that%20cleaning%20milking%20equipment%20between%20cows%20and%20outfitting%20workers%20with%20protective%20gear%20could%20help%20prevent%20the%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20workers%20are%20down%20in%20a%2C%20usually%2C%20recessed%20area%20and%20the%20udder%20is%20at%20face%20height%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20for%20their%20comfort%20and%20ability%20to%20work%20at%20milking%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20but%20it%20puts%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20milk%20splashing%20into%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22worker%20wearing%20a%20blue%20apron%20grey%20hoodie%20and%20baseball%20cap%20milks%20cows%20on%20a%20ledge%20putting%20the%20udders%20at%20eye%20level%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667ef0fdd1c84a0eaca8e194%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkers%20tend%20to%20cows%20in%20the%20milking%20parlor%20at%20a%20farm%20in%20Clinton%2C%20Maine.%3Cp%3ERobert%20F.%20Bukaty%2FAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoggles%20and%20face%20shields%20could%20help.%20For%20now%2C%20they%20are%20not%20common%20practice%20on%20the%20dairy%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20forms%20of%20protective%20gear%2C%20such%20as%20N95%20masks%2C%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20implement%20on%20dairy%20farm%20floors%20because%20of%20hot%20and%20humid%20conditions%2C%20Davis%20said.%20That%20can%20make%20heavy%20protective%20gear%20incredibly%20uncomfortable%20or%20even%20put%20workers%20at%20increased%20risk%20of%20heat-related%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20cleaning%20the%20milking%20equipment%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20processes%20for%20cleaning%2C%20but%20the%20level%20of%20disinfection%20that%20you%20need%20in%20order%20to%20inactivate%20virus%20is%20generally%20going%20to%20be%20beyond%20what%20might%20be%20normal%20practice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20cleaning%20process%20may%20look%20different%20farm-to-farm%20depending%20on%20the%20transmission%20dynamics%2C%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20different%20cows%20there%2C%20and%20how%20finicky%20the%20animals%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20pauses%20for%20cleaning%20in%20between%20milkings%20can%20affect%20how%20much%20milk%20a%20cow%20produces%20and%20even%20be%20harmful%20to%20the%20animal%2C%20Davis%20said.%20It%20could%20also%20result%20in%20longer%20exposure%20periods%20for%20workers%20because%20it%20takes%20longer%20to%20milk%20a%20lineup%20of%20cows.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20consumer%20side%20of%20the%20dairy%20industry%2C%20the%20study%20is%20also%20further%20evidence%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-eggs-meat-milk-dairy-safety-during-outbreak-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enobody%20should%20drink%20raw%20(unpasteurized)%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-cows-milk-spread-study-suggests-how-to-stop-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719658082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667ef26640cf2af6e4f6cf6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-cows-milk-spread-study-suggests-how-to-stop-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Raw%20milk%20is%20a%20hazard%20to%20cows%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20consumers%2C%20a%20new%20study%20suggests.%20There%20a%20few%20things%20dairy%20farms%20can%20do%20about%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40businessinsider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-cows-milk-spread-study-suggests-how-to-stop-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Space%20junk%3A%20What%20is%20it%20and%20how%20does%20it%20affect%20us%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719657928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111362845%2Cimgsize-35004.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Fspace-junk-what-is-it-and-how-does-it-affect-us%2Farticleshow%2F111362469.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SCIENCE%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Fspace-junk-what-is-it-and-how-does-it-affect-us%2Farticleshow%2F111362469.cms%22%2C%22cdnA