t%20through%20those%20years%2C%20there%20were%20people%20who%20did%20not%20give%20me%20a%20break%20because%20of%20what%20I%20looked%20like%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20evaluation%20I%20remember%20well.%20It%20was%20deemed%20that%20I%20didn't%20put%20anti-ice%20on%20quickly%20enough.%20That's%20not%20what%20I%20saw.%20But%20how%20do%20you%20say%20that%20decision%20was%20because%20I'm%20this%20or%20that%3F%20You%20don't%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20time%20I%20didn't%20100%25%20pass%20the%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224111d10-e367-4f65-a929-4ecb1c56fa0a%5C%22%3ECommercial%20pilots%20are%20qualified%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20seven%20years%20I%20left%20active%20duty%20and%20joined%20the%20reserves.%20In%201990%2C%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-pilot-pay-salary-american-delta-united-captain-first-officer-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20as%20a%20commercial%20pilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20United.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20routes%20were%20on%20a%20Boeing%20757%20out%20of%20Newark%2C%20mostly%20heading%20to%20Cape%20Town%2C%20Johannesburg%2C%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Captain%20Theresa%20Claiborne%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667954a740cf2af6e4f4e970%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Theresa%20Claiborne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20be%20a%20pilot%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20perseverant%20and%20a%20go-getter.%20You%20also%20need%20a%20thick%20skin%20because%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20there%20are%20still%20people%20who%20believe%20that%20we%20have%20no%20business%20flying%20airplanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%20out%20there%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fright-wing-commentators-