the%20financial%20years%202022-23%20and%202023-24%2C%20reveals%20that%20medical%20equipment%20and%20reagents%20worth%20%E2%82%B9660%20crores%20were%20acquired%20without%20any%20corresponding%20budget%20allocation.%20This%20revelation%20comes%20from%20a%20letter%20by%20the%20Accountant%20General%20to%20the%20Health%20Department%2C%20exclusively%20obtained%20by%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Findings%20of%20the%20Audit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audit%20found%20that%20the%20corporation%20purchased%20medical%20equipment%20and%20reagents%2C%20distributing%20them%20to%20776%20primary%20health%20care%20(PHC)%20facilities.%20Shockingly%2C%20more%20than%20350%20of%20these%20PHCs%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20technical%20manpower%20and%20storage%20facilities%20to%20effectively%20utilize%20the%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20audit%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Director%20of%20Health%20Services%20placed%20orders%20for%20these%20items%20without%20conducting%20essential%20baseline%20surveys%20or%20gap%20analyses%20to%20assess%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20each%20facility.%20The%20distribution%20was%20uniform%20across%20all%20PHCs%2C%20ignoring%20variations%20in%20patient%20load%20and%20specific%20requirements.%20This%20indiscriminate%20procurement%20has%20resulted%20in%20high-value%20equipment%20sitting%20idle%2C%20with%20the%20risk%20of%20deterioration%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20reagents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGround%20Report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Bhatgaon%20Primary%20Health%20Center%20in%20Raipur%2C%20sophisticated%20equipment%20like%20sonography%20and%20X-ray%20machines%20were%20procured%20but%20remain%20non-operational%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20specialist%20doctors.%20Dr.%20Harshita%20Tekam%20from%20the%20PHC%20noted%20that%20while%20basic%20services%20such%20as%20first%20aid%20and%20blood%20pressure%20monitoring%20are%20available%2C%20advanced%20machines%20cannot%20be%20used%20until%20