-valter-longo-eats-fasting-live-longer-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20Longevity%20Diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20created%20by%20his%20colleague%20and%20L-Nutra%20cofounder%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EValter%20Longo%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20gerontology%20and%20director%20of%20the%20USC%20Longevity%20Institute.%20It's%20mainly%20a%20plant-based%20diet%20but%20includes%20fish%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%2C%20plus%20lots%20of%20complex%20carbohydrates%2C%20and%20healthy%20fats%20from%20nuts%2C%20Antoun%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20similar%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplant-based-mediterranean-diet-add-ten-years-longevity-modeling-study-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20Diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20one%20study%20suggested%20could%20add%20up%20to%2010%20years%20to%20a%20person's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntoun%20shared%20three%20dietary%20principles%20he%20follows%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fessential-healthy-habits-for-your-twenties-thirties-longevity-advice-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20a%20long%2C%20healthy%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccc45353-b485-4204-9101-1a8d2f684573%5C%22%3EEat%20nuts%20every%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENuts%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotein-per-serving-animal-plant-based-foods-chart-comparison-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20complex%20carbs%2C%20and%20healthy%20fats%2C%20Antoun%20said.%20He%20eats%20them%20pretty%20much%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20breakfast%2C%20Antoun%20has%20nuts%20and%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20with%20a%20splash%20of%20oat%20or%20almond%20milk.%20He%20either%20has%20L-Nutra's%20Prolon%20Fasting%20bar%2C%20which%20is%20made%20of%20walnuts%2C%20almonds%2C%20macadamia%20nuts%2C%20and%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20honey%2C%20or%20just%20whole%20nuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOccasionally%20he%20has%20his%20company's%20Longevity%20Spread%2C%20which%20is%20made%20of%20mainly%20almonds%20and%20cocoa%20powder%2C%20on%20wholewheat%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20suggests%20that%20eating%20nuts%20regularly%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-young-people-can-lower-their-risk-for-heart-disease-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20the%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease.%3C%2Fa%3E%20A%20large%202017%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Cardiology%2C%20looked%20at%20data%20on%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20people%20across%2032%20years%20and%20found%20that%20those%20who%20ate%20nuts%20five%20or%20more%20times%20a%20week%20had%20a%2014%25%20lower%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease%20and%20a%2020%25%20lower%20risk%20of%20coronary%20heart%20disease%20than%20people%20who%20never%20or%20almost%20never%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuts%20have%20been%20found%20to%20lower%20the%20risk%20of%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20reduce%20%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20decrease%20the%20risk%20of%20blood%20clots%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20heart%20attack%20or%20stroke%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Mayo%20Clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223571c193-1e4b-4988-bea3-c668482b113b%5C%22%3EEat%20plant-based%20protein%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAntoun%20mainly%20eats%20plant-based%20protein%20including%20nuts%2C%20beans%2C%20and%20chickpeas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20compelling%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20a%20diet%20high%20in%20plants%20could%20boost%20longevity.%20In%20a%202023%20study%20published%20in%20JAMA%20Network%20Open%2C%2022%20pairs%20of%20twins%20were%20randomly%20assigned%20either%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvegan-diet-better-for-health-than-omnivore-identical-twins-study-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20healthy%20vegan%20diet%20or%20a%20hea