snubbed-as-captain-only-3-indians-in-cricket-australias-t20-world-cup-xi-5995938%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Frohit-sharma-snubbed-as-captain-only-3-indians-in-cricket-australias-t20-world-cup-xi-5995938%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Frohit-sharma-snubbed-as-captain-only-3-indians-in-cricket-australias-t20-world-cup-xi-5995938%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndira%20Gandhi%20Put%20Us%20In%20Jail%2C%20But%20Never%20Abused%20Us%26quot%3B%3A%20Lalu%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20Chief%20and%20former%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20on%20Saturday%20recalled%20what%20they%20went%20through%20during%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20Emergency%20and%20said%20that%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20put%20many%20of%20the%20leaders%20behind%20bars%2C%20but%20she%20never%20abused%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20shared%20on%20X%2C%20the%20RJD%20chief%20shared%20an%20article%20%26quot%3BThe%20Sangh%20Silence%20in%201975%26quot%3B%20written%20by%20him%20and%20journalist%20Nalin%20Verma.%20In%20the%20article%2C%20they%20attacked%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20and%20said%20that%20although%201975%20is%20a%20stain%20on%20the%20country's%20democracy%2C%20let's%20not%20forget%20who%20doesn't%20respect%20the%20Opposition%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20steering%20committee%20that%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan--had%20constituted%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20excesses%20of%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20then%20PM%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20I%20was%20in%20jail%20under%20the%20Maintenance%20of%20Security%20Act%20(MISA)%20for%20over%2015%20months.%20My%20colleagues%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20many%20of%20the%20BJP%20ministers%20speaking%20about%20the%20Emergency%20today.%20We%20hadn't%20heard%20of%20Modi%2C%20J%20P%20Nadda%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20PM's%20other%20ministerial%20colleagues%20who%20today%20lecture%20us%20on%20the%20value%20of%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndira%20Gandhi%20put%20many%20of%20us%20behind%20bars%2C%20but%20she%20never%20abused%20us.%20Neither%20she%20nor%20her%20ministers%20called%20us%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bunpatriotic%26quot%3B.%20She%20never%20enabled%20vandals%20to%20defile%20the%20memory%20of%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar--the%20architect%20of%20our%20Constitution.%201975%20is%20a%20stain%20on%20our%20democracy%20but%20let's%20not%20forget%20who%20doesn't%20respect%20the%20Opposition%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RJD%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2025%2C%201975%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20imposed%20a%2021-month%20state%20of%20emergency.%20This%20year%20marks%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Emergency%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20controversial%20periods%20in%20India's%20political%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20addressed%20the%20joint%20sitting%20of%20the%20Parliament%20and%20criticised%20the%20imposition%20of%20'Emergency'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmergency%20was%20the%20biggest%20and%20darkest%20chapter%20of%20the%20direct%20attack%20on%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20entire%20country%20plunged%20into%20chaos%20during%20the%20Emergency%2C%20but%20the%20nation%20was%20victorious%20against%20such%20unconstitutional%20powers%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20of%20the%20President%20have%20triggered%20reactions%20from%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20National%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20attempting%20to%20gain%20cheap%20applause%20by%20making%20th