ndrachud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719651312000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F08%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1712553551-688.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-morality-essential-to-india-s-diversity-cji-chandrachud-124062900310_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CJI%20Chandrachud%20elaborated%20on%20the%20notion%20of%20Constitutional%20Morality'%20as%20a%20restraining%20factor%20on%20the%20state%20that%20should%20derive%20from%20the%20Preambluar%20values%20of%20the%20Constitution%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-morality-essential-to-india-s-diversity-cji-chandrachud-124062900310_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-morality-essential-to-india-s-diversity-cji-chandrachud-124062900310_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-morality-essential-to-india-s-diversity-cji-chandrachud-124062900310_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGrave%20Danger%26quot%3B%20In%20Equating%20Court%20With%20Temple%2C%20Judge%20With%20God%3A%20Chief%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20equating%20judges%20with%20God%20is%20dangerous%20since%20the%20task%20of%20judges%20is%20to%20serve%20public%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20very%20often%2C%20we%20are%20addressed%20as%20Honour%20or%20as%20Lordship%20or%20as%20Ladyship.%20There%20is%20a%20very%20grave%20danger%20when%20people%20say%20that%20the%20court%20is%20a%20temple%20of%20justice.%20There%20is%20a%20grave%20danger%20that%20we%20perceive%20ourselves%20as%20the%20deities%20in%20those%20temples%2C%26quot%3B%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20Regional%20Conference%20of%20National%20Judicial%20Academy%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20that%20he%20feels%20reticent%20when%20he%20is%20told%20that%20the%20court%20is%20the%20temple%20of%20justice%20because%20the%20temple%20postulates%20that%20the%20judges%20are%20in%20the%20position%20of%20a%20deity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20rather%20recast%20the%20role%20of%20the%20judge%20as%20a%20server%20of%20the%20people.%20And%20when%20you%20regard%20yourselves%20as%20people%20who%20are%20there%20to%20serve%20others%2C%20then%20you%20bring%20in%20the%20notion%20of%20compassion%2C%20of%20empathy%2C%20of%20judging%20but%20not%20being%20judgmental%20about%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20even%20while%20sentencing%20anyone%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%2C%20the%20judges%20do%20that%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20compassion%2C%20since%20at%20the%20end%2C%20a%20human%20being%20is%20being%20sentenced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20these%20concepts%20of%20constitutional%20morality%2C%20which%20I%20think%2C%20are%20the%20key%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20or%20the%20High%20Court%20but%20also%20for%20the%20district%20judiciary%20itself%2C%20because%20the%20engagement%20of%20the%20common%20citizens%20begins%20first%20and%20foremost%20with%20the%20district%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20he%20strongly%20stressed%20on%20the%20relevance%20of%20technology%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20language%20is%20the%20central%20barrier%20to%20accessing%20and%20understanding%20verdicts%20by%20common%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20can%20provide%20us%20with%20some%20answers.%20Most%20judgments%20are%20written%20in%20English.%20Technology%20has%20enabled%20us%20to%20translate%20them.%20We%20are%20translating%2051%2C000%20judgments%20in%20other%20languages%2C%26quot%3B%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719650700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbktnod18_cji-dy-chandrachud-ians_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrave-danger-in-equating-court-with-temple-judge-with-god-chief-justice-5995494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20equating%20judges%20with%20God%20is%20dangerous%20since%20the%20task%20of%20judges%20is%20to%20serve%20public%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrave-danger-in-equating-court-with-temple-judge-with-god-chief-justice-5995494%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrave-danger-in-equating-court-with-temple-judge-with-god-chief-justice-5995494%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrave-danger-in-equating-court-with-temple-judge-with-god-chief-justice-5995494%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%8BNagarjuna%20calls%20Big%20B%20original%20mass%20hero%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719650616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111360622%2Cimgsize-35688.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnagarjuna-praises-kalki-2898-ad-calls-amitabh-bachchan-original-mass-hero%2Farticleshow%2F111360328.cms%22%2