nicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fanand-mahindra-cheers-for-team-india-may-the-flatten-the-opposition-in-the-final-again%2Farticleshow%2F111360348.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Orange%20Alert'%20Issued%20For%20Delhi%20Amid%20Warning%20Of%20Heavy%20Rain%20In%20Coming%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20is%20likely%20to%20receive%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20said%20today%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20monsoon%20arrived%20in%20the%20city%20with%20the%20heaviest%20downpour%20in%2088%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20has%20issued%20an%20'orange'%20alert%20for%20heavy%20rain%20for%20the%20next%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20is%20likely%20to%20receive%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20with%20an%20even%20heavier%20spell%20anticipated%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IMD%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20Delhi%2C%20including%20Rohini%20and%20Burari%2C%20received%20rainfall%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20has%20forecast%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20rain%20accompanied%20with%20thunderstorms%20over%20the%20next%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%2C%20moderate%20rain%20is%20defined%20as%20rainfall%20amounting%20to%20between%207.6%20and%2035.5%20mm%20in%20a%20day%2C%20and%20heavy%20rain%20is%20rainfall%20amounting%20to%20between%2064.5%20and%20124.4%20mm%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20recorded%20a%20minimum%20temperature%20of%2028%20degrees%20Celsius%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20maximum%20temperature%20is%20likely%20to%20settle%20around%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20the%20IMD%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20humidity%20levels%20stood%20at%2080%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20was%20recorded%20in%20the%20'moderate'%20category%20with%20a%20reading%20of%20108%20at%209%20am%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%20zero%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20'good'%2C%2051%20and%20100%20'satisfactory'%2C%20101%20and%20200%20'moderate'%2C%20201%20and%20300%20'poor'%2C%20301%20and%20400%20'very%20poor'%2C%20and%20401%20and%20500%20'severe'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20raining%20devastation%20on%20a%20city%20ill-prepared%20for%20a%20three-hour%20downpour%20that%20led%20to%20the%20roof%20of%20Delhi%20airport's%20Terminal-1%20collapsing%2C%20killing%20one%20person%20and%20suspending%20flight%20operations%2C%20and%20inundated%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20others%20were%20killed%20in%20rain-related%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20recorded%20228.1%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20highest%20since%201936%20for%20the%20month%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%2C%20228.1%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20was%20recorded%20at%20Safdarjung%2C%20the%20city's%20primary%20weather%20station%2C%20192.8%20mm%20at%20Lodhi%20Road%2C%20Mausam%20Bhavan%2C%20150.4%20mm%20at%20Ridge%2C%20106.6%20mm%20at%20Palam%2C%20and%2066.3%20mm%20at%20Ayanagar.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719649680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fneg1adig_delhi-rain-delhi-waterlogging-ani_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Forange-alert-issued-for-delhi-amid-warning-of-heavy-rain-in-coming-days-5995561%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20is%20likely%20to%20receive%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20the%20In