F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fvideo-close-shave-for-woman-after-she-falls-under-moving-train-in-ranchi-5995705%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSouth%20Africa%20Ko%20Choke%20Karaana%20Hoga%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-India%20Star%20Ahead%20Of%20T20%20WC%20Final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20country%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20Saturday%20when%20team%20India%20meet%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20India%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20end%20their%2013-year%20trophy%20drought%20whereas%20the%20Proteas%20will%20be%20hoping%20to%20win%20their%20first-ever%20ICC%20tournament.%20The%20South%20African%20team%20is%20making%20its%20first-ever%20appearance%20in%20the%20final%20of%20an%20ICC%20tournament%20whereas%20India%20will%20be%20hoping%20to%20look%20past%20the%20ghosts%20of%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20and%20hopefully%20win%20their%20first-ever%20trophy.%20Many%20have%20labelled%20the%20South%20African%20team%20as%20'chokers'%20for%20their%20previous%20inability%20to%20make%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20tournament%20whereas%20Indian%20fans%20have%20also%20had%20experience%20with%20the%20word%20given%20their%20loss%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20IANS%2C%201983%20World%20Cup-winning%20all-rounder%20Kirti%20Azad%20has%20stated%20what%20India's%20game%20plan%20needs%20to%20be%20like%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20talk%20about%20South%20Africa%20as%20it%20is%20their%20first%20time%20in%20the%20final%20of%20any%20ICC%20tournament.%20They%20were%20even%20called%20'chokers'%20as%20they%20used%20to%20always%20choke%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20which%20is%20why%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20predict%2C%20to%20say%20how%20they%20will%20perform%20in%20the%20final.%20But%20yes%20they%20will%20give%20it%20their%20best%20to%20win%20and%20India%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20to%20not%20get%20too%20complacent%20and%20we%20don't%20end%20up%20choking%20the%20game.%20The%20hope%20will%20be%20that%20we%20put%20up%20a%20good%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20saw%20the%20pitches%20last%20time%20out%20in%20the%20semifinals%2C%20the%20ball%20was%20not%20bouncing%20too%20much%20and%20staying%20low.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20and%20give%20them%20a%20good%20target.%20South%20Africa%20ko%20choke%20karaana%20hoga%20(We%20will%20have%20to%20get%20South%20Africa%20to%20choke)%2C%26quot%3B%20Azad%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20bowling%20attack%20has%20been%20brilliant%20from%20the%20very%20first%20game%20with%20Axar%20Patel%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20having%20been%20the%20stars%20of%20the%20tournament.%20Their%20stellar%20performances%20were%20in%20the%20spotlight%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20as%20they%20restricted%20the%20English%20batsman%20from%20chasing%20the%20171-run%20target%20and%20bundled%20their%20opponents%20out%20for%20103.%20Axar%20Patel%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20picked%20up%20three%20wickets%20each%20whereas%20Bumrah%20added%20two%20wickets%20to%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20is%20also%20a%20very%20important%20player%20for%20the%20side%20as%20the%20Indian%20skipper%20has%20scored%20248%20runs%20for%20his%20team%20throughout%20the%20tournament%20making%20him%20the%20third-highest%20run-getter%20in%20this%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20full%20belief%20that%20the%20way%20the%20Indian%20team%20is%2C%20we%20will%20perform%20well%20and%20win%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20performance%20by%20all%20players%20have%20been%20top-notch%2C%20especially%20the%20bowlers%20in%20the%20likes%20of%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Axar%20Patel%20have%20been%20bowling%20well.%20India's%20bowling%20attack%20is%20second%20to%20none.%20The%20biggest%20plus%20point%20for%20our%20side%20is%20the%20way%20Rohit%20is%20bat