Ffive-army-soldiers-in-tanks-swept-away-while-crossing-river-in-ladakh-124062900188_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Rules%20Set%20For%20SIM%20Card%20Replacement%20Under%20Mobile%20Portability%20From%20July%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmendments%20to%20Mobile%20Number%20Portability%20(MNP)%20regulations%20to%20check%20SIM%20swap%20and%20replacement%20fraudulent%20activities%20will%20come%20into%20force%20from%20July%201%2C%20The%20telecom%20regulatory%20body%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(TRAI)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(TRAI)%2C%20on%20March%2014%2C%202024%2C%20issued%20the%20Telecommunication%20Mobile%20Number%20Portability%20(Ninth%20Amendment)%20Regulations%2C%202024%2C%20which%20will%20come%20into%20force%20on%20July%201%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20regulator%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20TRAI%2C%20the%20SIM%20swap%20or%20replacement%20means%20a%20process%20of%20acquisition%20of%20a%20new%20SIM%20card%20in%20place%20of%20a%20lost%20or%20non-working%20SIM%20card%20by%20the%20existing%20subscriber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20TRAI%20rules%2C%20users%20can%20also%20choose%20the%20Mobile%20Number%20Portability%20(MNP)%20facility%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20retain%20their%20mobile%20number%20when%20they%20move%20from%20one%20access%20provider%20to%20another%20access%20provider%20in%20the%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ecountry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20view%20to%20improving%20the%20MNP%20process%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20the%20Telecommunication%20Mobile%20Number%20Portability%20Regulations%2C%202009%20have%20been%20amended%20eight%20times%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TRAI%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20introduce%20an%20additional%20criterion%20for%20rejection%20of%20the%20request%20for%20allocation%20of%20the%20Unique%20Porting%20Code%20through%20these%20amendment%20regulations.%20It%20further%20mandates%20that%20the%20UPC%20should%20not%20be%20allocated%20if%20the%20request%20for%20UPC%20has%20been%20made%20before%20the%20expiry%20of%20seven%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20SIM%20swap%20or%20replacement%20of%20the%20mobile%20number%20which%20was%20earlier%20ten%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20explanation%20note%2C%20the%20telecom%20regulator%20stated%20that%20while%20some%20stakeholders%20believed%20that%20a%2010-day%20wait%20period%20following%20a%20SIM%20swap%20or%20replacement%20was%20appropriate%2C%20others%20argued%20that%20a%20shorter%20wait%20period%2C%20such%20as%20two%20to%20four%20days%2C%20would%20be%20more%20reasonable%20and%20that%20a%2010-day%20wait%20period%20may%20cause%20subscribers%20inconvenience%2C%20particularly%20in%20cases%20of%20urgent%20porting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20amendment%20regulations%20are%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20the%20porting%20of%20mobile%20numbers%20by%20way%20of%20fraudulent%20SIM%20swap%2Freplacement%20by%20unscrupulous%20elements%2C%20TRAI%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719645180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd6po3k5g_sim-card-sim-cards-generic-ians_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-rules-set-for-sim-card-replacement-under-mobile-number-portability-from-july-1-5994794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amendments%20to%20Mobile%20Number%20Portability%20(MNP)%20regulations%20to%20check%20SIM%20swap%20and%20replacement%20fraudulent%20activities%20will%20come%20into%20force%20from%20July%201%2C%20The%20telecom%20regulatory%20body%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(TRAI)%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia