0final%2C%20Manjrekar%20looking%20at%20the%20broader%20picture%2C%20is%20more%20focused%20on%20the%20team's%20performance%20rather%20than%20a%20single%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20really%20concerned%20about%20Virat%20Kohli's%20form%20because%20the%20team's%20form%20is%20far%20more%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%2C%20who%20features%20as%20an%20expert%20on%20'Caught%20and%20Bold'%20show%20on%20Disney%20Hotstar%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20seven%20matches%2C%20Kohli%2C%20with%20all%20his%20experience%2C%20has%20struggled%20to%20find%20that%20elusive%20purple%20patch%20and%20put%20together%20a%20string%20of%20performances%20while%20opening%20alongside%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20IPL%202024%20he%20racked%20up%20a%20mouth-watering%20tally%20of%20741%20runs%2C%20but%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20he%20mustered%20up%20just%2075%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2010.71%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Kohli's%20no-show%2C%20India%20rose%20as%20a%20collective%20unit%2C%20with%20a%20different%20player%20emerging%20as%20a%20matchwinner%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rohit%20leading%20the%20team%20with%20a%20fearless%20approach%20from%20the%20front%2C%20Manjrekar%20firmly%20believes%20that%20India%20can%20end%20their%20hiatus%20of%20ICC%20World%20Cup%20trophies%20because%20of%20the%20new%20template%20that%20they%20introduced%2C%20which%20has%20worked%20like%20a%20charm%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20India%20can%20lift%20the%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20India%20has%20discovered%20a%20new%20template%2C%20the%20modern%20template%20of%20playing%20T20%20cricket%2C%20and%20it's%20paying%20rich%20dividends%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20a%20battle%20of%20unbeaten%20sides%20after%20South%20Africa%20and%20India%20stormed%20into%20the%20final%20without%20conceding%20a%20single%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjrekar%2