-enjoying-their-time-at-space-station-iss%2Famp_articleshow%2F111353997.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20Will%20Probably%20Jump%20Into%20Barbados%20Ocean%20If...%3A%20Sourav%20Ganguly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20will%20be%20playing%20a%20second%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20eight%20months%20when%20it%20takes%20on%20South%20Africa%20in%20Barbados%20in%20the%20summit%20clash%20of%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20mega%20event%20on%20Saturday.%20India%20lost%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20final%20of%202023%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20on%20November%2019%20despite%20reaching%20the%20summit%20clash%20with%20an%20unbeaten%20tag.%20Now%2C%20the%20side%20will%20be%20having%20another%20chance%20to%20end%20its%20long%20wait%20of%20ICC%20title%20drought%20when%20it%20faces%20the%20Proteas%20in%20the%20final%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20hilariously%20said%20that%20Rohit%20might%20jump%20in%20the%20Barbados%20ocean%20if%20India%20lose%20the%20upcoming%20final%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20played%20two%20World%20Cup%20finals%20where%20he%20has%20gone%20into%20the%20final%20unbeaten.%20That%20speaks%20of%20his%20captaincy%20and%20leadership%20quality%20and%20I'm%20not%20surprised%20because%20he%20became%20captain%20when%20I%20was%20the%20BCCI%20president%20and%20when%20Virat%20didn't%20want%20to%20captain%20India%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ganguly%20as%20quoted%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20make%20him%20captain%20because%20he%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20captain.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20pushing%20from%20all%20of%20us%20to%20make%20him%20captain%20and%20I'm%20very%20happy%20to%20see%20the%20progress%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20under%20him.%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20said%20winning%20IPL%20titles%20could%20sometimes%20be%20more%20challenging%20because%20of%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20has%20the%20record%20of%20winning%20five%20IPL%20titles%2C%20which%20is%20a%20huge%20achievement.%20Winning%20an%20IPL%20sometimes%20is%20more%20difficult.%20Don't%20misquote%20me%2C%20I'm%20not%20saying%20IPL%20is%20better%20than%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20you%20have%20to%20win%2016-17%20(12-13)%20matches%20to%20win%20an%20IPL%3B%20here%20you%20need%20to%20win%208-9%20matches%20to%20win%20a%20World%20Cup.%20The%20honour%20is%20more%20in%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20Rohit%20does%20it%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20he%20can%20lose%20two%20World%20Cup%20finals%20in%20seven%20(six)%20months.%20He%20will%20probably%20jump%20into%20the%20Barbados%20ocean%20if%20he%20loses%20two%20finals%20under%20his%20captaincy%20in%20seven%20months.%20He%20has%20led%20from%20the%20front%2C%20batted%20brilliantly%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20it%20continues%20tomorrow.%20Hope%20India%20finishes%20on%20the%20right%20side%2C%20and%20they%20should%20play%20with%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20the%20best%20side%20of%20the%20competition.%20I%20wish%20them%20luck%2C%20I%20wish%20they%20win.%20Hope%20they%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20luck%20tomorrow%20because%20that%20is%20required%20to%20win%20big%20tournaments%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719627000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Frdj4mie8_india-afp_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fif-india-lose-to-south-africa-in-t20-wc-final-rohit-sharma-will-probably-jump-into-barbados-ocean-sourav-ganguly-5990994%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20India