7.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika1-1719549336-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika1-1719549336-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika1-1719549336-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika1-1719549336-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354723%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmarika%20runs%20Dhara%20Krishi%20Farm%20with%20her%20father%20and%20brother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmarika%20realised%20that%20vegetable%20farming%20would%20be%20more%20profitable%20than%20paddy%2C%20and%20she%20slowly%20started%20experimenting%20with%20the%20same%20on%20their%20land.%20The%20results%20were%20astonishing%20and%20resulted%20in%20two%20things%20%E2%80%94%20a%20switch%20to%20vegetable%20farming%20on%20over%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20Smarika%20quitting%20her%20job%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20farmer%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20she%20claims%20to%20have%20received%20a%20production%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20of%20tomato%20per%20acre%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20in%20the%20previous%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20why%20you%20should%20grow%20vegetables!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%20have%20longer%20growth%20cycles%20which%20are%20generally%20twice%20a%20year.%20Vegetable%20farming%2C%20however%2C%20gives%20multiple%20harvests%20as%20the%20growth%20cycles%20are%20shorter%20and%20are%20more%20profitable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVegetable%20farming%20offers%20a%20triple%20win%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%