element-caption%5C%22%3ESmarika%20has%20grown%20tomato%20in%20over%2013%20acres.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimproving%20the%20soil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20adding%20cow%20dung%20and%20vermicompost.%20We%20just%20left%20the%20soil%20free%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20basking%20in%20the%20sunlight.%20We%20installed%20fences%20and%20ensured%20that%20the%20drainage%20system%20was%20in%20place%20and%20the%20land%20was%20sloping%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smarika%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20installed%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system.%20After%20this%2C%20she%20prepared%20a%20raised%20bed%20for%20tomatoes%20and%20mulches%20(a%20layer%20of%20material%20applied%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20an%20area%20of%20soil%20to%20conserve%20soil%20moisture%20and%20improve%20fertility).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20and%20researching%20over%20the%20weekends%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20Smarika%20took%20the%20plunge%20into%20full-time%20farming.%20With%20seeds%20purchased%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20the%20Chandrakar%20family%20prepared%20for%20their%20first%20tomato%20harvest%20in%202021.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20a%20great%20harvest%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20in%20the%20first%20year.%20We%20sold%20it%20in%20local%20%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marts)%20and%20in%20other%20cities%20like%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Patna%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20more.%20I%20have%20tied-up%20with%20brokers%20with%20whom%20I%20pre-decide%20the%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20tomatoes%2C%20she%20also%20grows