eering%2C%20he%20initially%20juggled%20his%20studies%20with%20managing%20the%20family%20farm.%20At%2018%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20first%20year%20of%20college%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20and%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20farm%20fell%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20manage%20both%20the%20farm%20and%20my%20studies%20simultaneously.%20That%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20manage%20our%20expenses.%20I%20had%20no%20choice.%20I%20am%20the%20eldest%20son%20of%20my%20family%20and%20I%20had%20to%20look%20after%20my%20younger%20sister%20and%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biju%20grows%20a%20variety%20of%20exotic%20fruits%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354134%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBiju%20grows%20a%20variety%20of%20exotic%20fruits%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20he%20ventured%20into%20the%20corporate%20world%