farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20it%2C%20Neetu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20not%20just%20to%20create%20an%20escape%20for%20adults%20but%20also%20a%20space%20for%20the%20kids%20to%20explore%20nature.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20kids%20are%20drinking%20milk%20out%20of%20cartons%20and%20eating%20chicken%20from%20KFC.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20create%20an%20organic%20space%2C%20an%20organic%20lifestyle%20for%20not%20only%20our%20daughter%20but%20for%20all%20the%20kids%20we%20could%20offer%20it%20to.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20that%20we%20serve%20to%20the%20guests%20comes%20from%20our%20farms.%20We%20even%20make%20our%20own%20oil%20from%20walnuts%2C%20groundnuts%20and%20mustard%20seeds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeetu%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20produce%20our%20own%20honey%20with%2023%20bee%20boxes.%20We%20grow%20turmeric%20and%20chia%20seeds%20and%20have%20our%20own%20dairy%20for%20milk.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20maintain%20a%20small%20poultry%20farm%20with%20around%2030%20chickens%20for%20eggs.%20Vegetables%20are%20sourced%20from%20local%20farms%20as%20well.%20Essentially%2C%20everything%20we%20consume%20here%20is%20either%20grown%20or%20raised%20by%20us%20or%20sourced%20from%20the%20organic%20farms%20nearby.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302308%2Fbengaluru-couple-grows-organic-food-forest-using-permaculture-build-sustainable-mud-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20follows%20a%20no-waste%20policy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20use%20everything%20that%20we%20procure.%20All%20the%20food%20waste%20becomes%20fodder%20for%20our%20livestock.%20All%20the%20cow%20dung%20is%20converted%20and%20made%20into%20organic%20incense%20sticks%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20homestay%20itsel